WEBVTT

02:13.920 --> 02:15.480
Why is my magic gone?

02:19.920 --> 02:21.120
Wu Shiguang?

02:25.280 --> 02:26.400
Let's talk inside.

02:43.800 --> 02:45.640
Why'd you grab a kid?

02:49.200 --> 02:50.720
I found him in the river.

02:53.520 --> 02:55.840
Want some tea? Pour it yourself.

03:01.800 --> 03:03.360
What's going on?

03:03.440 --> 03:04.920
Where are we exactly?

03:05.960 --> 03:08.320
In an old illusion inside the Star Stone.

03:08.400 --> 03:11.320
And now we're living
as people from the past.

03:13.400 --> 03:16.760
An illusion?
Did your master tell you that?

03:23.920 --> 03:26.640
Why does your master
know the Star Stone so well?

03:27.680 --> 03:30.760
My master understands
all things in the world.

03:30.840 --> 03:32.080
And he taught me a lot.

03:32.160 --> 03:33.280
Alright.

03:34.000 --> 03:34.960
Then where's my partner?

03:36.760 --> 03:38.760
Probably the same as us,

03:39.360 --> 03:42.720
but maybe she's in a different past.

03:43.680 --> 03:45.800
I just hope she got a better family.

03:48.280 --> 03:50.240
This one's way too poor.

03:50.320 --> 03:52.520
This family has such bad luck.

03:53.440 --> 03:55.560
So how do we leave this illusion?

03:55.640 --> 03:58.680
We need the Star Stone here
to leave the illusion.

03:59.480 --> 04:02.360
But it is the Aodeng tribe's treasure.

04:02.440 --> 04:03.480
It's hidden away.

04:04.080 --> 04:05.920
Only the chieftain knows where it is.

04:07.560 --> 04:08.880
That's easy.

04:09.920 --> 04:12.840
Di Zhu's father
will be back in three days.

04:12.920 --> 04:14.320
We can ask him using Word Magic.

04:15.640 --> 04:19.680
Besides, you said a hundred years here
is just a moment out there.

04:20.720 --> 04:23.600
Staying here a couple of days
should be fine, right?

04:26.480 --> 04:28.480
Hey, Know-Something,
how much longer can you hold on?

04:28.560 --> 04:30.360
Seems like it could break any moment!

04:32.200 --> 04:33.560
You called me Know-It-All earlier.

04:34.520 --> 04:36.440
Now it's Know-Something?

04:37.040 --> 04:39.640
Maybe he thinks
you're weaker than you look.

04:39.720 --> 04:41.640
He's just trying
to stir trouble, Master Bai Ze.

04:41.720 --> 04:42.680
Don't listen to him.

04:44.000 --> 04:45.160
You look really worn out.

04:45.240 --> 04:47.240
Is there anything I can do?

04:47.320 --> 04:51.000
The illusion inside the Star Stone
flows at a different speed than we do.

04:51.080 --> 04:54.200
A thousand days inside
is just a blink out here.

04:55.200 --> 04:58.400
So, even if I can only
hold on for a short while,

04:58.480 --> 05:00.400
I can buy them a hundred years inside.

05:01.000 --> 05:04.600
Bai Ze, you know everything in the world.

05:04.680 --> 05:08.040
How could you forget
the disasters that happened here?

05:09.120 --> 05:11.280
Disasters? What disasters?

05:11.360 --> 05:14.840
Goddess Nuwa once prophesied
that four disasters would strike here.

05:14.920 --> 05:17.400
A great fire that burns everything,

05:17.480 --> 05:19.640
a devastating storm
that destroys the world,

05:19.720 --> 05:21.520
a meteor shower that levels all,

05:21.600 --> 05:24.680
and a deadly freeze that withers all life.

05:25.280 --> 05:27.400
The first disaster, the great fire,

05:27.480 --> 05:30.680
was the heavenly fire
brought by the falling star.

05:30.760 --> 05:32.160
After that,

05:32.800 --> 05:36.440
the other three disasters
all happened too.

05:36.520 --> 05:38.080
The guys inside the Star Stone

05:39.160 --> 05:42.520
are not far from these disasters.

05:43.480 --> 05:47.200
So their time is running out.

05:48.240 --> 05:52.680
SEVEN DAYS
UNTIL THE HURRICANE CATASTROPHE

05:52.760 --> 05:55.160
1,000 YEARS AGO

05:55.240 --> 05:56.200
Oh, right.

05:56.880 --> 05:58.920
The stone paintings said

05:59.000 --> 06:01.320
you and I are bound by a troubled fate.

06:01.400 --> 06:03.480
If we get married successfully,

06:03.560 --> 06:06.880
then the Star Stone will be my dowry,
right in our hands.

06:06.960 --> 06:08.920
It's Man Man marrying Di Zhu.

06:09.520 --> 06:11.640
We're Man Man and Di Zhu now.

06:12.400 --> 06:15.000
We're fated ones.
We're a pair wherever we go.

06:16.840 --> 06:20.320
Isn't your fated one Ji Ling?

06:24.240 --> 06:27.000
You've muttered about him
countless times in your dreams.

06:30.840 --> 06:32.280
How do you know?

06:35.000 --> 06:36.200
Did you sneak a peek at me at night?

07:02.920 --> 07:03.920
Ji Ling…

07:07.960 --> 07:09.440
my fated one…

07:31.440 --> 07:32.960
I'm not Ji Ling.

07:33.880 --> 07:36.960
Your seduction tricks won't work on me.

07:39.520 --> 07:41.200
Ji Ling once said that too.

07:48.400 --> 07:51.280
You can wear any skin you want,

07:52.080 --> 07:55.360
but your heart can't be faked.

07:59.760 --> 08:05.120
What you see now is all fake.
Don't get too deep into the act.

08:06.440 --> 08:10.000
But to get the Star Stone,
you really do have to marry me.

08:18.080 --> 08:19.480
See, you're practically drooling.

08:20.120 --> 08:22.600
Come on, have a taste.

08:22.680 --> 08:23.800
It smells so good.

08:27.240 --> 08:30.000
One more time, I'm a vegetarian.

08:31.680 --> 08:34.640
Quit pretending. Fine, don't eat then.

09:01.880 --> 09:07.240
TWENTY-FOUR HOURS UNTIL THE METEOR BLAST

09:07.320 --> 09:10.760
150 YEARS AGO

09:11.280 --> 09:13.080
Yuan Xizai, what are you even doing?

09:13.160 --> 09:16.160
Your mind-control tricks won't work on me!

09:16.240 --> 09:18.840
Today's our only chance
to get the Star Stone.

09:18.920 --> 09:20.920
Time's running out. Stop messing around!

09:27.200 --> 09:28.520
How is he?

09:30.120 --> 09:31.320
Put it on!

09:33.080 --> 09:35.560
He hit his head. He should be fine.

09:48.160 --> 09:49.920
This is Green Ape territory?

09:50.000 --> 09:51.160
Yeah.

09:52.680 --> 09:55.400
We just wiped out
the human reinforcements stationed here.

09:56.720 --> 09:57.840
We…

09:59.440 --> 10:00.960
wiped out humans?

10:03.200 --> 10:04.640
We're not human?

10:05.400 --> 10:06.600
We are…

10:09.520 --> 10:11.440
high-rank Green Ape demons.

10:19.760 --> 10:22.960
FIFTY YEARS UNTIL THE GREAT FREEZE

10:23.040 --> 10:25.040
100 YEARS AGO

10:25.120 --> 10:27.200
So where do we look for the Star Stone?

10:28.640 --> 10:29.560
I don't know.

10:30.960 --> 10:32.520
Besides what my master told me,

10:33.240 --> 10:37.440
in my memory,
the Star Stone never appeared.

10:38.840 --> 10:39.920
But that's okay.

10:40.840 --> 10:42.240
We have enough time.

10:47.760 --> 10:49.080
For what?

10:55.720 --> 10:57.000
Finding the Star Stone.

10:58.040 --> 11:01.520
Wu Zhiqi, if they don't get
the real Star Stone,

11:02.120 --> 11:04.080
then its power won't be activated.

11:05.040 --> 11:08.600
And your people will just keep sleeping.

11:09.160 --> 11:10.600
You're lying to me.

11:10.680 --> 11:14.920
If even I can lie,
then there's no truth in this world.

11:15.520 --> 11:18.840
Master Bai Ze, you know all things.

11:19.720 --> 11:21.200
You must have another way, right?

11:22.320 --> 11:24.040
There is indeed one more way.

11:25.000 --> 11:28.640
A place might connect
to the Star Stone illusion.

11:29.320 --> 11:32.360
But to open the exit,
we need someone's blood.

11:32.440 --> 11:35.640
Whose? I'll rally my weasels…

11:35.720 --> 11:38.280
I mean, my Weasel brothers.

11:38.360 --> 11:41.520
Wherever he is,
I'll find him and bleed him dry.

11:41.600 --> 11:43.080
Just say the name.

11:43.160 --> 11:45.400
Leave the rest to me.

11:46.000 --> 11:47.400
-Wu Shiguang.
-What?

11:49.520 --> 11:52.280
Hey, Know-Nothing. Are you serious?

11:55.640 --> 11:57.920
Got it! I know where to find
Wu Shiguang's blood!

11:58.000 --> 11:59.760
You're up, You Chi.

11:59.840 --> 12:03.080
Get Wu Shiguang's blood,
then risk opening the exit.

12:03.760 --> 12:05.040
Risk it?

12:06.600 --> 12:07.960
All by myself?

12:46.240 --> 12:49.040
So, we're a married couple now.

12:50.400 --> 12:51.840
That's right.

12:51.920 --> 12:55.000
I'm the chief of the Flood Dragon clan,
named Cang Hao.

12:56.000 --> 12:57.280
You're my…

13:00.920 --> 13:02.120
wife.

13:02.640 --> 13:03.720
Your name's Qing Yi.

13:03.800 --> 13:04.760
Got it, darling.

13:06.240 --> 13:07.760
You call it "darling" here, right?

13:13.920 --> 13:16.680
This child is different from others here.
It has no horns.

13:17.840 --> 13:19.400
Let's see if it's a boy or girl.

13:19.480 --> 13:21.520
No need to look. It's a boy.

13:22.280 --> 13:25.080
How do you know? How can you be sure?

13:25.680 --> 13:26.840
-How do you…
-It's me!

13:26.920 --> 13:29.840
It… It's me! Wu Shiguang!

13:47.480 --> 13:48.880
Shiguang baby.

13:50.720 --> 13:52.360
Can you not call him that?

13:53.360 --> 13:54.880
Then what should I call him?

13:54.960 --> 13:56.920
I'm little Shiguang's mother now.

13:57.000 --> 13:58.760
I'll call him whatever I want.

13:58.840 --> 14:00.760
You're lucky I didn't go with "brat".

14:02.680 --> 14:03.920
Hi, brat…

14:06.440 --> 14:08.680
This illusion is really something.

14:09.320 --> 14:10.960
I'm your mother now?

14:11.720 --> 14:14.080
Is it because grown-up you is so annoying,

14:14.160 --> 14:18.200
so you send little Shiguang
to make yourself look a little better?

14:19.080 --> 14:20.520
What's wrong with grown-up me?

14:21.520 --> 14:22.520
Not handsome enough?

14:23.680 --> 14:24.840
The looks are okay.

14:25.880 --> 14:29.800
The personality, though…
went a bit crooked.

14:37.800 --> 14:42.320
If you see a demon
with a heart-shaped, wavy birthmark,

14:42.840 --> 14:44.880
bring them back immediately.

14:47.600 --> 14:49.160
Your birthmark is pretty interesting.

14:49.920 --> 14:51.640
Looks like a heart made of flowing water.

14:52.760 --> 14:54.120
How come I never noticed it before?

14:54.840 --> 14:58.520
I wear a painted skin to hide my identity,
so others can't see it.

15:08.240 --> 15:09.640
Where are you going?

15:12.200 --> 15:14.000
To find the Star Stone, of course.

15:15.080 --> 15:18.040
Or do you really plan
to stay here with me like a loving couple,

15:18.120 --> 15:18.960
grow old together?

15:20.840 --> 15:22.240
What about the kid?

15:22.840 --> 15:25.880
Put him to sleep,
feed him, change his diapers.

15:25.960 --> 15:26.920
I can't do any of that!

15:27.520 --> 15:30.360
Isn't your master all-knowing?
Didn't he teach you?

15:31.880 --> 15:34.960
Wake up. This is an illusion.

15:35.560 --> 15:38.120
Just leave him here. He won't die.

15:38.720 --> 15:40.120
How can you be so cold?

15:41.040 --> 15:43.400
Let him go, and let us go too, okay?

15:43.480 --> 15:45.200
Business first.

15:47.680 --> 15:50.440
-No way!
-Isn't it all fake anyway?

15:51.920 --> 15:53.040
Still no!

16:16.320 --> 16:19.640
Bai Ze said lighting this talisman
is all it takes.

16:20.240 --> 16:23.040
Don't worry. I'll send
two people to protect you.

16:24.160 --> 16:27.080
Where are my helpers?
Where are my bodyguards?

16:50.240 --> 16:53.240
JIN ZHENG, POJUN
THE NORTHERN DIPPER HUNTER

16:53.320 --> 16:54.440
Watch out!

17:00.280 --> 17:03.600
HUA QI, TIANTONG
THE SOUTHERN DIPPER HUNTER

17:12.560 --> 17:13.880
Didn't expect to find one here.

17:13.960 --> 17:15.359
This trip was worth it.

17:15.440 --> 17:16.720
Is that something to be proud of?

17:16.800 --> 17:20.040
After a whole month,
we just stumbled upon one by accident.

17:20.800 --> 17:24.200
I miss the days
working with Senior Si Feng.

17:24.880 --> 17:26.280
The new generation surpasses the old.

17:26.359 --> 17:28.160
Appreciate who's in front of you, okay?

17:29.000 --> 17:30.080
Besides, how am I worse than her?

17:30.760 --> 17:33.200
You're worse in any way.

17:35.920 --> 17:37.560
You're such a bad senior.

17:38.280 --> 17:39.400
Stop right there!

17:44.800 --> 17:45.800
I'm just a low-rank demon.

17:45.880 --> 17:47.960
I haven't done anything terrible.

17:48.040 --> 17:50.040
At most, I steal a chicken now and then.

17:50.120 --> 17:54.000
Please, honored double-flower hunters,
go easy on me.

17:57.840 --> 18:02.440
Bai Ze did ask us to protect you,
but you don't have to bow so low.

18:10.360 --> 18:14.480
What? Master Bai Ze sent us here
to rob a grave?

18:16.000 --> 18:18.080
Who would just save someone's blood
for no reason?

18:18.160 --> 18:22.160
Even for a close friend,
that's pretty weird.

18:23.000 --> 18:25.560
When you first joined the Shilin Sect,

18:25.640 --> 18:29.600
you took evil demons' heads,
claws, and teeth as trophies,

18:29.680 --> 18:30.560
filling your whole room.

18:30.640 --> 18:33.280
Sometimes, you even slept hugging them.

18:33.360 --> 18:35.040
If we're talking weird…

18:35.120 --> 18:41.120
Hey, great double-flower hunters,
you just stand there and watch?

18:41.200 --> 18:42.360
Don't your consciences bother you?

18:42.440 --> 18:44.440
Is this how Bai Ze told you to help me?

18:44.520 --> 18:47.680
What he said was to protect you.

18:48.280 --> 18:50.680
Helping you costs extra.

19:05.760 --> 19:07.640
Why are you stealing from the dead?

19:08.160 --> 19:09.760
This is my own stuff.

19:11.240 --> 19:13.080
You buried it here
for yourself in advance?

19:13.160 --> 19:14.400
Nonsense!

19:16.320 --> 19:19.440
This is the first thing
I ever stole from the human world

19:19.520 --> 19:21.880
when I turned 16.

19:22.480 --> 19:25.640
For us weasels, the first thing
we steal is extremely important!

19:25.720 --> 19:27.640
It represents our name for life!

19:27.720 --> 19:30.000
Look what you stole. A ruler!

19:30.880 --> 19:32.360
Look what Wu Shiguang did!

19:32.440 --> 19:34.360
Father, don't expect me to be a legend.

19:34.440 --> 19:36.760
He's on another level. I can't match that.

19:36.840 --> 19:39.880
Besides, I'm just a little weasel.

19:40.600 --> 19:43.440
Stealing a ruler isn't so bad.
You only stole a cane yourself.

19:43.520 --> 19:44.680
You dare talk back?

19:47.800 --> 19:50.920
Our weasel family motto is,
"Do your best."

19:51.600 --> 19:53.240
Don't force it.

19:53.320 --> 19:56.520
As long as you have no regrets.

20:00.360 --> 20:03.280
I'll never forget
your kindness in raising me.

20:04.080 --> 20:07.240
But I have to avenge this blood debt.

20:07.320 --> 20:09.920
So I must venture into the human world.

20:10.680 --> 20:11.600
Sir,

20:13.240 --> 20:14.200
take care.

20:18.280 --> 20:20.200
You brat, don't do anything reckless.

20:20.280 --> 20:22.160
The human world is very dangerous.

20:32.160 --> 20:33.040
Don't worry.

20:35.760 --> 20:40.120
Listen, no fighting while I'm away.
Don't worry your father.

20:40.720 --> 20:41.760
Off you go.

20:42.880 --> 20:43.840
Go…

20:51.080 --> 20:51.920
Go…

21:09.320 --> 21:12.280
I'm worried about you. Let me go with you!

21:14.600 --> 21:16.200
But the human world is very dangerous.

21:16.280 --> 21:18.000
That's right. So I'm going with you.

21:18.080 --> 21:19.240
With us together,

21:19.320 --> 21:22.720
this very dangerous human world
is only half as dangerous for you!

21:25.480 --> 21:29.720
Besides, I've even made us
a cool partnership name.

21:30.520 --> 21:33.240
We'll be… the Wu-Chi Duo!

21:37.560 --> 21:38.640
How about that?

21:39.520 --> 21:40.960
Where's your ruler?

21:43.360 --> 21:44.600
I left it with my father.

21:44.680 --> 21:47.480
In case he misses me.
Seeing it is like seeing me.

22:21.480 --> 22:24.400
Behind those shifty eyes, you're so loyal?

22:25.080 --> 22:26.240
Of course!

22:28.400 --> 22:32.520
Hey, these are big, bright eyes!

22:36.120 --> 22:39.080
Found it. That's it.

22:40.040 --> 22:42.440
An enchanted animal trap.

22:43.080 --> 22:44.680
Watch out!

22:45.520 --> 22:46.680
Wu Shiguang!

22:48.720 --> 22:50.040
Your leg!

22:52.240 --> 22:55.600
Thanks to Wu Shiguang pushing me away,
or I'd be dead.

22:56.400 --> 23:00.120
But back then, out of nowhere,
a ball of white light suddenly appeared

23:00.200 --> 23:02.120
and protected Wu Shiguang.

23:03.200 --> 23:04.560
So he didn't die either.

23:04.640 --> 23:06.920
We're really buddies in misfortune.

23:07.000 --> 23:08.320
Enough with the talk now?

23:09.280 --> 23:11.840
Delay any longer, your buddy
might run into real misfortune.

23:47.160 --> 23:48.240
What are you doing?

23:48.320 --> 23:50.840
Humming. Do you like it?

23:55.280 --> 23:56.160
He probably likes it.

23:58.840 --> 24:00.000
He's you.

24:00.080 --> 24:02.080
You like it.

24:02.680 --> 24:04.120
Do you like me…

24:05.400 --> 24:06.760
humming?

24:11.600 --> 24:13.160
Getting shy already?

24:13.240 --> 24:14.720
Then what will you do
when we sleep without clothes tonight?

24:14.800 --> 24:16.480
Nonsense!

24:16.560 --> 24:18.240
What decent person sleeps without clothes?

24:25.280 --> 24:26.320
Don't come closer.

24:35.040 --> 24:38.200
We each have our own quilt,
and it's thicker than anything.

24:39.520 --> 24:41.240
I'm a girl, and I don't even mind.

24:41.320 --> 24:43.240
And you're complaining?

24:46.040 --> 24:49.400
I saw you couldn't sleep,
so I'm just keeping you company.

24:59.200 --> 25:02.320
This place… was once my home,

25:03.840 --> 25:05.800
with my happiest memories,

25:07.040 --> 25:08.880
my dearest family,

25:10.040 --> 25:11.880
and everything from my childhood.

25:14.680 --> 25:16.880
Even knowing this is an illusion,

25:17.680 --> 25:20.080
I'm still overwhelmed by mixed emotions.

25:22.640 --> 25:24.400
It's like having

25:25.640 --> 25:29.560
a very, very… sad dream.

25:30.600 --> 25:34.760
When I saw that baby in the swaddle,
moonlight shining on him,

25:35.560 --> 25:39.600
I recalled my father said
he named me Shiguang

25:40.480 --> 25:42.560
because the day he found me,

25:43.160 --> 25:47.720
it was like finding a light
that brought them warmth and joy.

25:49.560 --> 25:51.400
He hoped my future

25:54.000 --> 25:55.440
to be colorful,

25:56.960 --> 25:58.520
peaceful, and bright.

26:06.960 --> 26:09.640
So you want to stay
and take care of this child,

26:11.360 --> 26:15.200
just like your father and mother
took care of you.

26:39.040 --> 26:43.280
My mother never slept well,
always had nightmares.

26:44.960 --> 26:49.520
I remember my father, just like this,
would gently pat her shoulder.

27:03.280 --> 27:05.160
Let's look for the Star Stone tomorrow.

30:06.920 --> 30:08.120
Man Man!

30:09.240 --> 30:11.200
Wake up! Get up!

30:11.280 --> 30:12.360
What's wrong?

30:12.440 --> 30:13.880
We've got a problem.

30:13.960 --> 30:14.920
Let's go.

30:20.040 --> 30:23.160
-What happened?
-This person just died.

30:34.120 --> 30:35.960
How dare you cancel
my wedding with Man Man?

30:36.040 --> 30:41.960
Di Zhu, ever since Man Man came here,
three of our people have died!

30:42.040 --> 30:44.360
Such a bringer of disaster cannot stay!

30:44.960 --> 30:47.120
My father is the chieftain.
He's the one who decides.

30:47.200 --> 30:48.080
You…

30:49.720 --> 30:51.840
When did you become so disrespectful?

30:52.440 --> 30:54.080
Sir, please give me three more days.

30:54.160 --> 30:55.720
Within three days,

30:55.800 --> 30:58.760
I will find the real killer
and prove my innocence.

30:58.840 --> 31:00.080
And if you don't?

31:00.880 --> 31:02.400
Then burn Man Man alive.

31:06.280 --> 31:09.080
Burn me too. I'll die with him!

31:11.160 --> 31:12.400
Touched, huh?

31:22.080 --> 31:23.640
Coming through!

31:24.400 --> 31:25.640
Excuse me.

31:26.280 --> 31:28.400
Hello. Have you seen this?

31:29.040 --> 31:30.120
No, I haven't.

31:30.720 --> 31:31.720
Have you seen this?

31:41.360 --> 31:44.200
-Have you seen this?
-No.

31:44.280 --> 31:46.760
-Have you seen this?
-No.

31:46.840 --> 31:48.320
There, there!

31:52.160 --> 31:55.360
Be good now. Mother will be right back.

31:59.840 --> 32:02.120
Come here. Give me a hand.

32:02.200 --> 32:03.880
He needs to eat his porridge.

32:03.960 --> 32:05.360
Easy now.

32:05.440 --> 32:06.320
There, there.

32:06.400 --> 32:07.760
Porridge is coming!

32:07.840 --> 32:08.760
Come on.

32:13.000 --> 32:15.040
Come on. Be good now.

32:16.160 --> 32:17.760
Mother's back, isn't she?

32:48.880 --> 32:50.400
Hey, getting busy?

32:50.480 --> 32:51.640
Easy now.

32:52.920 --> 32:54.480
We're back!

32:54.560 --> 32:56.080
-Mother!
-Go to your mother.

33:29.400 --> 33:30.880
He's actually a demon!

33:31.400 --> 33:34.360
I found out last night.
He's from the Chameleon Snake clan.

33:34.440 --> 33:36.960
They change color to blend in.

33:37.520 --> 33:39.160
They're masters of concealment.

33:41.440 --> 33:43.760
Man Man, you got an itch or what?

33:51.480 --> 33:54.720
Da Ji and the other victims
were all killed by snake venom.

33:56.200 --> 33:57.880
Leave it to me.

34:15.760 --> 34:17.199
I'm not the killer.

34:17.920 --> 34:20.600
I came to Aodeng
only to find the Star Stone.

34:21.239 --> 34:22.840
I haven't killed anyone.

34:27.639 --> 34:29.199
So it's not him?

34:33.440 --> 34:38.639
Forget everything, leave Aodeng,
and never come back.

34:59.640 --> 35:02.640
If it's not him, then who could it be?

35:03.960 --> 35:05.240
Snake venom…

35:10.800 --> 35:13.320
Don't tell me it's you, Little Nine?

35:30.000 --> 35:33.080
Relax. The blood didn't turn black.

35:33.840 --> 35:36.560
Looks like it's not Little Nine.

35:41.360 --> 35:46.000
Our delicate and precious Master Chi Wen
testing the poison in my place?

35:46.720 --> 35:48.000
I'm so touched.

35:53.960 --> 35:55.200
Are you Ji Ling?

35:59.480 --> 36:01.000
You're so obsessed with Ji Ling?

36:01.800 --> 36:03.800
You have to prove I'm him?

36:07.280 --> 36:09.160
Even if Ji Ling is a puppet,

36:09.840 --> 36:12.200
where did his South Mountain
fox memories come from?

36:13.320 --> 36:17.120
Fake memories
don't have that many details.

36:22.840 --> 36:24.200
What are you doing?

36:25.280 --> 36:27.080
Trying to know your secret.

36:29.280 --> 36:31.320
Indeed a defenseless boy.

36:32.080 --> 36:33.360
You have no sacred power now.

36:33.440 --> 36:35.560
You can't resist my Word Magic.

36:35.640 --> 36:37.960
What a perfect chance.
How could I waste it?

36:38.040 --> 36:39.640
I suggest you stop.

36:40.240 --> 36:44.360
If you dare disrespect me, I'll… I'll…

36:44.440 --> 36:45.800
What?

36:48.080 --> 36:52.960
With that expression,
you're just asking for it.

37:01.000 --> 37:02.440
Where is my magic?

37:06.120 --> 37:09.560
You can't seem to control your power too.

37:10.520 --> 37:14.800
Even if you use Word Magic,
my answer won't change.

37:15.400 --> 37:16.760
I am not Ji Ling.

37:19.280 --> 37:20.640
But just now…

37:22.760 --> 37:26.160
I tested the poison for you
because I knew I'd be fine.

37:27.200 --> 37:28.920
The killer's target is the Star Stone.

37:29.760 --> 37:32.680
All the victims
were people who loved Di Zhu.

37:32.760 --> 37:36.400
Di Zhu, I won't give up on you!
You and the Star Stone are both mine!

37:39.000 --> 37:40.320
Figured it out?

37:41.440 --> 37:42.400
Yeah.

37:43.360 --> 37:46.720
If the killer means to eliminate
competitors for the Star Stone,

37:46.800 --> 37:51.120
then Man Man should be his primary target.

37:52.480 --> 37:55.960
Snake venom can kill mortals,
but it can't kill demons.

37:56.560 --> 37:57.680
Exactly.

37:57.760 --> 38:02.480
Even if Little Nine were the killer,
its venom couldn't kill me.

38:02.560 --> 38:05.800
So… I dared to test it for you.

38:41.320 --> 38:42.880
How's it going on your end?

38:43.920 --> 38:47.560
People keep dying, and no killer found.

38:47.640 --> 38:49.240
Ao Erlie returns tonight.

38:49.320 --> 38:50.880
You need to hurry.

38:52.720 --> 38:53.840
I know.

38:55.280 --> 38:56.520
Why are you so quiet today?

38:57.280 --> 38:59.720
Acting all solemn and mature.

38:59.800 --> 39:03.160
Do the girls of Aodeng
like this cold attitude?

39:06.040 --> 39:09.680
The more on my mind,
the less I feel like talking.

39:10.840 --> 39:13.960
Look at you, so relaxed.
What are you folding?

39:15.320 --> 39:19.040
My younger brother was always sickly
and stayed home all the time.

39:19.800 --> 39:21.680
He folded paper lanterns
in all sorts of shapes.

39:22.480 --> 39:23.600
Did you forget?

39:25.280 --> 39:26.760
Of course I remember.

39:26.840 --> 39:29.000
He taught you how to make
these paper lanterns, right?

39:31.280 --> 39:35.520
Whenever I miss him, I fold one.

39:36.280 --> 39:39.720
Di Zhu, how can you be so happy now?

39:40.280 --> 39:42.200
If the real killer
isn't caught in three days,

39:42.280 --> 39:44.320
you and Man Man will be burned alive.

39:48.280 --> 39:50.960
Yeah. "Live together, die together"?

39:51.560 --> 39:53.440
That's just a story to fool girls.

39:54.120 --> 39:58.600
I don't like him enough to die for him.

40:00.760 --> 40:03.720
Being burned alive with someone so cold?

40:04.760 --> 40:05.800
That's way too tragic.

40:07.480 --> 40:08.960
We're worlds apart.

40:10.360 --> 40:11.560
No way.

40:14.720 --> 40:16.520
Di Zhu! The chieftain is back.

40:16.600 --> 40:17.960
He's asking for you!

40:21.960 --> 40:24.480
Okay. Got it.
